THE NOMOS × NIDA CONVERGENCE
V2 is where NOMOS stops being a concept and becomes deployed infrastructure. Every business on the platform publishes a machine-readable service contract. Every AI agent — consumer-side and business-side — consumes these contracts to auto-negotiate and auto-execute. Nida becomes the first live implementation of the NOMOS protocol in a real marketplace with real money flowing through it. This is how you prove NOMOS works — not with a whitepaper, but with thousands of autonomous transactions running on executable governance contracts.


